M 
<emphasis box="[449,944,687,711]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="2956">
m) (from Timor 
<collectingRegion box="[632,691,688,711]" country="Cameroon" name="East" pageId="38" pageNumber="2956">Leste</collectingRegion>
, Dili, 
<date box="[761,931,687,711]" pageId="38" pageNumber="2956" value="2005-02">February 2005</date>
).
</emphasis>
Body length 2150. Head, length 190; median width 180; postocular setae 62. Pronotum, length 146; width 284; major setae am 40, aa 28, ml 38, epim 62, pa 70. Fore wing length 800; sub-basal setae 48, 52, 70. Tergite IX setae S1 125, S2 125, S3 120. Tube length 120; basal width 65; anal setae 145. Antennal segments III–VIII length 48, 54, 50, 44, 40, 30.
</paragraph>
